        // If p[p_idx] is already greater than head_right_reach, this head cannot cover p_idx.
        // If p[p_idx] is less than head_left_reach, this head cannot cover p_idx.
        // So, we need p[p_idx] to be in [head_left_reach, head_right_reach].

