    // The total number of nestings in the initial configuration is n - k (total dolls - number of chains).
    // Out of these, 'correct_consecutive_pairs' are useful.
    // So, (n - k) - correct_consecutive_pairs nestings must be undone.
    // Each undo operation costs 1 second.

